title: James Taylor looking to push Test claims after earning England recall - York Press
text:
James Taylor is determined to prove he belongs in England's Test team as he relishes his belated second shot at the big time in international cricket. He must still oust an incumbent to force his way back in again on the three-match tour against Pakistan in the United Arab Emirates, but there is something about Taylor's busy adaptability that suggests he must come into the reckoning in these extreme climes.
 York Press.
